description:
Maria Polushkin Robbins, &quot;The One-Dish Vegetarian: 100 Recipes for Quick and Easy Vegetarian Meals&quot;

English | ISBN: 0312181515, 0312254032 | 1999 | EPUB | 182 pages | 3,7 MB

This text contains more than 100 meatless dishes. Maria Robbins has taken the techniques and delicious flavours of the world's best cuisines, including Creole, Chinese, Mexican, Italian and Moroccan, to create recipes that will please steadfast and occasional vegetarians alike. The dishes include: linguine with spring vegetables; Indonesian vegetable curry; brown rice and lentil salad; risotto with eggplant and pineapple; bean and corn chilli; and dozens more. From pasta, curries and stir-fries to risotto, soups, grain dishes and light but filling salads, these recipes are low in fat and cholesterol and high in fibre.
